# Factorio Report

## EXISTING STRUCTURES

### Lab at position(x)
The lab is currently not powered and requires automation science packs to complete research.

## ERROR TIPS

### Errors when placing new poles
- Ensure that you are passing a valid Prototype object when attempting to place a new pole. Verify the object type before placement.

### Errors when placing wooden chests
- Ensure that you are passing a valid Prototype object when attempting to place a wooden chest. Verify the object type before placement.

### Errors related to lab power
- Check the power supply to the lab. Ensure that it is connected to a power source to function properly.

### Errors when lacking required items for research
- Ensure you have the necessary ingredients, specifically 10 automation science packs, to complete the ongoing research.
